Description: Defines the underlying file structure for a 'RAVE' pipeline;
    provides high-level class definition to build, compile, set, execute, 
    share, and serialize pipeline objects with language support on both R and 
    'Python'; offers mark-down and 'shiny' dashboard templates for extending
    and building customized pipelines. See the full paper by Magnotti, 
    Wang, and Beauchamp (2020, <doi:10.1016/j.neuroimage.2020.117341>), or 
    check 'citation("ravepipeline")' for details.
